cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image classification using CNN models, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper proposes a new loss function to improve the discriminability of features and the classifier's strength, which involves machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural networks (cs.NE).
